See Entry requirements to find out what you will need to do when you arrive in Croatia.
Travel in Croatia
Lockdown restrictions have largely been lifted. You should follow the latest instructions from the local authorities here.
Face masks
It is mandatory for passengers to wear masks on public transport, taxis, shops and other commercial premises.
